These are Puzzles for 3x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-1::.
5 different games are played: monopoly, canasta, backgammon, domino, scrabble
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, azure, purple, aquamarine, blood-red
There are 5 different nationalities: german, chinese, indian, thai, brazilian
 1. the person who likes red is the person playing domino##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4
 3. the person playing canasta is the german##1
 4. the brazilian is between the person who likes red and the person playing scrabble##2
 5. the person who likes red is on the right of the brazilian##1
 6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 7. the person who likes azure is on the far left##1
 8. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
 9. the thai is on the right of the chinese##1
10. the person who likes blood-red is the brazilian##1
11. the brazilian is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
12. the indian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |      5      |
| Game         | canasta    | backgammon  | scrabble | monopoly    | domino |
| Color   | azure     | purple   | aquamarine | blood-red | red   |
| Nationality         | german | chinese | thai  | brazilian | indian        |

