.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: thriller, martial-arts, disaster, horror, western
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, dahlia, tulip, bellflower, orchid
House: townhouse, cottage, victorian, colonial, ranch-style
 1. the victorian house is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who growsorchid is between the townhouse house and the colonial house##2
 3. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 6. the person watching thriller movies is in the middle##1
 7. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person watching disaster movies##1
 8. the person who growsdahlia is on the far left##1
 9. the victorian house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
10. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
11. the person who growsbellflower is between the ranch-style house and the cottage house##2
12. the colonial house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |        2        |     3      |         4          |     5     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror    | martial-arts         | thriller | western        | disaster   |
| Flower     | dahlia | tulip | bellflower  | orchid | balloon-flower |
| House   | victorian       | ranch-style      | colonial   | cottage           | townhouse      |

