.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-3::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: apricot, blood-red, emerald, blue, mauve
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian, japanese, thai, chinese
The people have 5 different hobbies: board-games, chess, skydiving, rock-climbing, drawing
 1. the person who likes blood-red is the chinese##1
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is the egyptian##1
 3. the person who likes blue is in the middle##1
 4. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
 5. the person who likes apricot is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who likes mauve##2
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who likes blue is on the right of the chinese##1
 8. the argentine is on the far right##1
 9. the thai is in an even position##4
10. the person who likes emerald is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
11. the argentine is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the egyptian and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2     |     3      |       4       |     5      |
| Color    | emerald | blood-red    | blue   | apricot          | mauve      |
| Nationality       | japanese    | chinese | egyptian       | thai | argentine |
| Hobby   | drawing     | rock-climbing     | chess | board-games          | skydiving     |

