.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-4::.
There are 5 different nationalities: italian, french, turkish, british, spanish
City: rome, venice, colone, edinburgh, san-francisco
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rowing, cycling, snowboarding, skiing, baseball
 1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the turkish##3
 4. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
 5. the french is on the far right##1
 6. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the italian##3
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 8. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an even position##4
10. the person who's sport is baseball is in an odd position##4
11. the italian is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |
| Nationality   | italian     | spanish    | turkish  | british | french |
| City           | edinburgh | venice    | colone | san-francisco  | rome    |
| Sport     | baseball      | snowboarding | skiing    | cycling    | rowing    |

