.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: zombie, spy, western, crime, fantasy
5 different pets are kept: bird, horse, ferret, frog, rat
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, chaman, davidoff, fonseca, pall-mall
 1. the chaman-smoker is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 3. the davidoff-smoker is in an even position##4
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is the owner of the frog##1
 5. the fonseca-smoker is between the bolivar-smoker and the person watching fantasy movies##2
 6. the person watching spy movies is in the middle##1
 7. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 8. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 9. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
10. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
11. the person watching crime movies is the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |    5    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | zombie        | spy    | western      | crime  |
| Pet   | frog | ferret    | bird | horse | rat |
| Cigar     | chaman   | fonseca | bolivar | davidoff      | pall-mall   |

