 3. the fan of pop is in an odd position##4
 4. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
 5. the person traveling to boston is in an odd position##4
 6. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
 8. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
 9. the person traveling to rome is between the fan of metal and the person driving the scooter##2
10. the fan of folk is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |      3       |    4     |    5     |
| Music-Genre         | metal   | punk  | pop      | folk  | salsa   |
| City   | boston | rome   | liverpool     | marseilles | venice  |
| Transport         | motorbike       | ship | scooter | trike  | skateboard |

