.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-20::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, ritmeester, siglo, cain, pall-mall
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, adventure, horror, martial-arts, family
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, marigold, iris, dahlia, orchid
 1. the person who growsiris is in an even position##4
 2. the ritmeester-smoker is in an even position##4
 3. the person who growsorchid is in an odd position##4
 4. the person watching adventure movies is between the cain-smoker and the ritmeester-smoker##2
 5. the game-smoker is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 6. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
 7. the person who growsiris is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 8. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who growsdahlia and the person who growsiris##2
10. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person who growsorchid is in an odd position##4
12. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
13. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1
14. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
15. the person who growsamaryllis is in an odd position##4

